{"type": "article", "id": 8862, "title": "Wakē 只叫醒你的闹钟", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-24T07:27:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235209Y2LtQE6Zrmke7iwV.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t集体生活中，大概很多人都有过想设闹钟又害怕影响到别人的尴尬。来自洛杉矶的 Lucera Labs 最近推出了一款只把使用者叫醒，而不影响他人的闹钟，闹钟工作的原理是利用渐变灯光这种最为温和的方式叫醒你，但这束光只会射向你一个人。同时，它能够在设定起床时间感应用户的体热，通过旋转锁定用户。向你一个人发送声波。这款闹钟售价 249 美元，目前正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，可以<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/58395680/wake-welcome-to-the-dawn-of-bedroom-robotics\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052352064dzHvbhqfPL3JAQG.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235206uoMEaRHZy4D6VOkG.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235207yJjsWEDIzxAeOugv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235207IZlx6Y4251L8TJQE.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.99117647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235208Lf3uTt5DYZ0BcaMI.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.30441176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235208vnzXEaBAQYWj3c7L.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.77058824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}